Westminster Hall debates take place in Grand Committee Room located on upper level off the north west corner of Westminster Hall. You don't need invitation.   <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Hi <a href="/JWhittingdale" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="129569947"><s>@</s><b>JWhittingdale</b></a> The MP for Maldon in 1383 was so unpopular the townspeople kidnapped &amp;ransomed his servants :/ <a href="https://t.co/BXqVi3gGrr" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://www.historyofparliamentonline.org/volume/1386-1421/constituencies/maldon" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="http://www.historyofparliamentonline.org/volume/1386-1421/constituencies/maldon"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://www.</span><span class="js-display-url">historyofparliamentonline.org/volume/1386-14</span><span class="invisible">21/constituencies/maldon</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a><a href="https://t.co/6D3yopS7TB" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/HistParl/status/923857769182187520" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/HistParl/status/923857769182187520"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/HistParl/statu</span><span class="invisible">s/923857769182187520</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Fantastic that we have had more than 190,000 responses to <a href="/hashtag/yourBBC?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>yourBBC</b></a> consultation. We will take full account in next stage of Charter Review</p>

          <a class="account-group js-account-group js-action-profile js-user-profile-link js-nav" href="/JWhittingdale" data-user-id="129569947">

    <span class="FullNameGroup">
      <strong class="fullname show-popup-with-id u-textTruncate " data-aria-label-part="">John Whittingdale</strong><span></span><span class="UserBadges"><span class="Icon Icon--verified"><span class="u-hiddenVisually">Verified account</span></span></span><span class="UserNameBreak"></span></span><span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr" data-aria-label-part="">@<b>JWhittingdale</b></span></a>

        
        <small class="time">

         <a class="js-initial-focus" target="_blank" href="http://support.twitter.com/articles/14226-how-to-find-your-twitter-short-code-or-long-code" rel="noopener">See SMS short codes for other countries</a>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </tfoot>
</table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
